---
import CtaButton from './../CtaButton.astro';
---

<section id="about" class="section about" aria-labelledby="about-title">
	<div class="section-inner">
		<p class="eyebrow">About Me</p>
		<div class="about-items">
			<article class="text-section" aria-labelledby="about-title">
				<h2 id="about-title">9+ years of experience</h2>
				<p>
					My name is Michał Zabrzyjewski and under the brand Interfejs, I provide high-end 
					frontend development, team leadership, and technical consulting. I've engineered solutions across diverse industries, scaling SaaS platforms 
					and tackling complex business challenges head-on. I thrive in the frontend ecosystem 
					because it sits right at the intersection of technical logic and creative 
					artistry, allowing me to build software that is both beautiful and performant.
				</p>
			</article>

			<article class="text-section text-section-right" aria-labelledby="about-leadership-title">
				<h2 id="about-leadership-title">Leadership & Collaboration</h2>
				<p>
					Over the years, I've led teams of engineers, worked closely with cross-functional 
					squads, and partnered with stakeholders to ship great software. 
					Whether taking full ownership as a sole contractor or driving results within Agile 
					and Scrum frameworks, I adapt quickly to any workflow. I champion proactive 
					communication because it's the ultimate tool for keeping technical execution aligned with business strategy.
				</p>
			</article>

			<article class="text-section" aria-labelledby="about-frontend-title">
				<h2 id="about-frontend-title">Versatile Frontend Expert</h2>
				<p>
					My core stack centers around <strong>React, TypeScript, and modern JavaScript</strong>, 
					but my adaptability extends to <strong>Vue, Ionic, and React Native</strong>. 
					I specialize in engineering complex, heavy-duty interfaces—ranging from scalable enterprise 
					platforms and data-driven SaaS products to highly interactive, custom web applications. 
					I bring deep expertise in state management and modern styling systems, ensuring every 
					solution is performant, maintainable, and scalable under the hood.
				</p>
			</article>
		</div>
	</div>
	<CtaButton
		href="#projects"
		ariaLabel="Scroll to case studies section"
		label="View Projects"
		immediate
	/>
</section>

<style>
  .section {
		position: relative;
    padding: clamp(56px, 7vw, 112px) 0;
  }

  .section-inner {
    width: min(1120px, calc(100% - 40px));
    margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 0 0 60px 0;
  }

  .about {
    border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    background: #f8fafc; 
  }

  .eyebrow {
    margin: 0 0 16px;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .about-items {
    display: grid;
    gap: clamp(64px, 10vh, 120px); 
    margin-top: 40px;
  }
  .text-section {
    max-width: 900px;
    width: 100%;
  }
  .text-section-right {
    margin-left: auto;
  }

  h2 {
    margin: 0;
    color: #111827;
    font-size: clamp(34px, 3vw, 60px);
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .text-section p:last-child {
    margin: 28px 0 0;
    color: #334155;
    font-size: clamp(18px, 2vw, 22px);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  @media (max-width: 820px) {
    .about-items {
      gap: 48px;
    }
    
    .text-section-right {
      margin-left: 0; 
    }
    
    .text-section {
      max-width: 100%;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 520px) {
    .section-inner {
      width: min(100% - 28px, 1120px);
    }
  }
</style>
